{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act34side_level_act34side_03_beg","storyGroup":"act34side","storySort":6,"storyDependence":"act34side_level_act34side_02_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BP-3","storyName":"如海雪纷散","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"随着调查深入，西昆妲与艾丽妮发现数据员的失踪似乎与深海教会有关。与此同时，前往海嗣巢穴投放信标的舰队遭到袭击，深海猎人紧急出城救援。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act34side/level_act34side_03_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act34side_03","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":4,"next":6,"characters":["？？？","海嗣","西昆妲","卡西娅","卢契拉","艾丽妮","克莱门莎","凯尔希","“小帮手”","乌尔比安","斯卡蒂","幽灵鲨","歌蕾蒂娅","军团士兵","海巡队队员"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"2","amount":"0","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"呼，呼——得赶快才行！","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"！","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"古球藻？这里怎么会出现古球藻，难道弥利亚留姆还有其他人在培育濒危藻类？","id":14},{"type":"dialog","id":15},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":16,"musicid":0},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":17},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":18},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":20},{"type":"dialog","id":21},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"80,0","duration":"1","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"1.15","id":23},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.6","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"80,0","posto":"80,-30","duration":"0.7","id":25},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":26},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#1$1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"团窗藻、石花膜、紫苔......","id":28},{"type":"dialog","id":29},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"80,-30","posto":"50,-30","duration":"0.5","id":30},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#4$1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"等等，这个色型的千灯英，这是我自己培育的......","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你们在街道上挣扎......还是太干燥了，你们会枯死的。","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这里发生了什么？有人对你们做了什么吗？","id":35},{"type":"dialog","id":36},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":37},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"50,-30","posto":"100,0","duration":"0.3","id":38},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":39},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#8$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你们要迁移到哪里？有人在......","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"等、等等！","id":42},{"type":"dialog","id":43},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"-200,0","duration":"1.5","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":44},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":45},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":47},{"type":"charslot","id":48},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":49},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#4$1","duration":"1","id":51},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"消失了？","id":53},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#3$1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这个管道口......","id":55},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#7$1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"唔！","id":57},{"type":"dialog","id":58},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"0,-150","duration":"1","id":59},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":60},{"type":"dialog","id":61},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_jump_water","id":62},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":64},{"type":"charslot","id":65},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sea","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":66},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":67},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":68},{"type":"bg","duration":"3","from":"1","to":"0","block":"false","id":69},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":71},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#5$1","duration":"1","id":72},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这里是......","id":74},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"15","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":75},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#7$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"咳咳，咕——","id":77},{"type":"dialog","id":78},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":79},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_divebubble","volume":"0.5","id":80},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":81},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#7$1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（是谁？为什么？）","id":83},{"type":"dialog","id":84},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":85},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rampartclose","volume":"0.1","id":86},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"3.5","xstrength":"3","ystrength":"2","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":87},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":88},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#5$1","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（好大的轰鸣......城市要开始移动了吗？）","id":90},{"type":"dialog","id":91},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":92},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_divebubble","volume":"0.5","id":93},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":94},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#6$1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（有东西在动——是谁在那里？）","id":96},{"type":"dialog","id":97},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":98},{"type":"charslot","id":99},{"type":"char","duration":"2.5","from":"1","to":"1","id":100},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1388_1#1$1","afrom":"0","ato":"0","posfrom":"0,-200","posto":"0,-200","id":101},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"0.8","duration":"0","id":102},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.18","fadetime":"0.01","id":103},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.18","fadetime":"0.01","id":104},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":105},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":106},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"2","id":107},{"type":"char","duration":"2","from":"1","to":"0.5","id":108},{"type":"bg","duration":"3","from":"0","to":"1","id":109},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"0.8","duration":"2","id":110},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,-200","posto":"0,-100","duration":"2","id":111},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":112},{"type":"char","duration":"2","from":"0.5","to":"0","id":113},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"1","duration":"2","id":114},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,-100","posto":"0,50","duration":"2","id":115},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":116},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_seabornattack","volume":"0.5","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"（愉悦地鼓胀液泡）","id":118},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":119},{"type":"dialog","id":120},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":121},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"2","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":123},{"type":"charslot","id":124},{"type":"char","from":"0","to":"0","id":125},{"type":"bg","from":"0","to":"0","id":126},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":127},{"type":"curtain","id":128},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":130},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":132,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":133},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":134},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":135},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"抱歉，希望不会耽误两位的工作。","id":137},{"type":"dialog","id":138},{"type":"charslot","id":139},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":140},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"没关系，我和卢契拉只是在对城市单元骨架进行例行检修和维护。","id":142},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......所以，还是没有图利娅的下落吗？","id":144},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"卢契拉，距离我们报案还没过多久。","id":146},{"type":"charslot","id":147},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"看得出来，两位对自己的这位朋友很关心。所以，图利娅最近是否有说起过自己遭遇了什么麻烦？","id":149},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"她胆子很小，不可能得罪什么人。","id":151},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"嗯，符合档案。她也没有向你们透露过有关航道计划或者信标数据的任何事情？","id":153},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"没有。","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"其实我们都算不上朋友，只是偶尔能说上几句话。她总是独来独往的，悄悄鼓捣些自己的东西。","id":156},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"等等，你们在怀疑图利娅？","id":158},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"对不起，可能在我的描述里，她听起来有些不对劲......","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"但、但她可能只是压力太大了。弥利亚留姆离开本境的这半年，几乎每天都在发生战斗，大家的神经都绷得很紧。","id":161},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"深海教会从未放弃过对航道计划的破坏。这段时间，我们已经清理了足够多的深海教徒。","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"那些堕落者在暴露之前，也不过是一个个平常的同胞。","id":164},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"可她没有任何理由......","id":166},{"type":"dialog","id":167},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#3$1","id":168},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":169},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#4$1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"唔，其实，我始终不太理解，那个孩子为什么会选择加入航道计划。","id":171},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"卡西娅女士，您的意思是？","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"图利娅之前在弥利亚留姆的生态艺术创作所工作，你们都知道，对吧？","id":175},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"这座城市从原本的停泊点撤离，又接到新的作战布置之后，生态艺术创作所很快就搬迁到了其他城市。","id":177},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#5$1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"她本来有机会随创作所去往其他城市，继续原本的事业，不是吗？但她却选择......","id":179},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"抱歉，我打断一下，各位所说的撤离？","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#6$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"卢契拉，这件事你的印象更深吧？那时候你还在穹顶工作，应该亲眼目睹了变故发生的全过程。","id":183},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......嗯。","id":185},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"那是阿戈尔规模最大的火山能源站之一，供养着无数科研设施。弥利亚留姆当时负责它的建设与防卫工作。","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"城市当时就停泊在那座能源站的下方，透过穹顶看过去，赤色的辉光恒久地照耀着方圆数十海里的水域。","id":188},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"能源站的热量吸引来了种类繁多的生物，那里有阿戈尔最大的濒危植物繁育基地。","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"弥利亚留姆的生态艺术事业，就依托这样得天独厚的环境蓬勃发展。","id":191},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"但那片辉光陷入了黑暗......","id":193},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#2$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"海嗣？","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"嗯。","id":197},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#7$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"一年前，潮水般的海嗣顺着洋流抵达了那里，弥利亚留姆紧急撤离了。","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"失去了最重要的环境条件，生态艺术创作所不得不和其他相关机构一同搬迁至其他城市。","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"可是当时，城内驻扎着一支完整的军团，我们本来有机会夺回那座能源站。","id":201},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"那时，航道计划的战争指令刚刚下达，弥利亚留姆的撤离其实是一次战略转移。","id":203},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我也是在那之后，随军团调来了弥利亚留姆。","id":205},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#5$1","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"许多同胞的生活轨迹都因此改变了......也包括卢契拉。","id":207},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"呃，我转岗从穹顶来地面，只是因为恐高......对不起，这不是重点。","id":209},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":210},{"type":"multiline","name":"西昆妲","text":"卡西娅女士，你是想说，图利娅加入航道计划的动机并不纯粹？","id":211},{"type":"multiline","name":"西昆妲","text":"这是很严重的指控。","id":212},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我也不相信。","id":214},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#6$1","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"不不，我只是将所知道的事情告诉你们而已。","id":216},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#5$1","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"长官，您无法否认的是......此刻，这座城市里有十多万军民，但并非所有人都真正参与到了航道计划之中。","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"许多人只是照常生活，并不理解我们最终要在海洋中开辟的，究竟是怎样的一条道路。","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"这位伊比利亚的客人，难道不也是为了了解航道计划，才从陆地来到海洋吗？","id":220},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"......","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"无论图利娅是否与深海教会存在瓜葛，她私自复制了航道计划的数据，这是事实。","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"只有找到她，所有的疑问才能得到解答。","id":225},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"可是，可是弥利亚留姆并不大，哪怕是藏在穹顶的夹层，或者循环系统的角落，也应该被找到了。","id":227},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"卢契拉小姐说得没错。图利娅很可能已经不在城内，但我们在城市周边的水域同样没有探测到她的生物信号。","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"港口枢纽没有计划外的舰艇出入，而只凭民用的深潜装置，图利娅不可能在短短数十个小时内离开我们的探测范围。","id":230},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"但......三十多个小时前，为了接应伊比利亚的使节团，城市本身进行过一次短途移动。如果就在那时......","id":232},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"你的意思是，图利娅是在那个时候......离开了城市？","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":235},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":236},{"type":"charslot","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":238},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":239},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":241},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":242},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"......所以，克丽斯腾，那位哥伦比亚科学家，突破了上万年来阻隔层对泰拉的封锁。","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"一年多以来，那个空洞始终没有完全合拢，在此期间，阿戈尔保持着对宇宙的观测。从结果来看，阻隔层之外还没有出现明显的异象。","id":245},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我曾尝试阻止克丽斯腾，但没有成功。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我们还有时间......但恐怕并不多了。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#6$1","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"以高密度的能量强行撕开电子云层——一种近乎蛮力的手段。我们此前并未在陆地上发现与之相匹配的能源。","id":250},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"克丽斯腾的手段与阿戈尔的技术是同源的，你们都受到先史文明的帮助或启发。","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"她在特里蒙地底发现了先史文明用以保存火种的石棺群，并取得了其管理者的信任。","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"凯尔希医生，离开本境前，我并未期待陆地上有您这般了解阿戈尔与先史的智者。","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"您再一次证明了，我们对泰拉的了解仍不充分。","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"久困于海渊的鳞会失去感光的能力。看来，哪怕国家已无力再支撑规模庞大的开拓计划，我们也不能停止对未知的探求。","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"星门、双月、天空中的阻隔层、地幔里的遗迹群......这颗行星仍然存在太多非自然的事物。","id":258},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#4$1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"甚至，我们的远洋舰队曾在行星另一面的漆黑浓雾当中，遥远地探测到一处极为特殊的地貌。","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"海流被突兀地截断，仿佛那里即是大洋的尽头。","id":261},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"那不过是一处早已冷却的温床。最核心的先史文明遗产就沉眠在阿戈尔的腹地，您对此心知肚明，执政官阁下。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"海床之下的先史遗迹是海洋对阿戈尔的馈赠。它孕育了阿戈尔的文明，赋予了你们远超陆上诸国的视界与能力。","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......以及，责任。","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"“责任”，如您所言，凯尔希医生。","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"陆地人从何时开始称自己为“人类”？当他们用源石点燃第一堆篝火？用土石筑起第一座城市？","id":268},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"大地上的自我认知与身份认同是在漫长的过程中自然建立的。时至今日，人们依然习惯以最狭隘的方式定义“人类”。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"但阿戈尔对人类身份的认知，却是被赋予的。我们与前人类并非同族，但在继承其衣钵的同时，自然也继承了其身份。","id":272},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"所以，阿戈尔自诞生起便负有责任——对人类的责任。海嗣不会使阿戈尔抛下责任，相反，它只会使责任越发沉重。","id":274},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"执政官阁下，您确实是最适合领导弥利亚留姆的执政官。","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#7$1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"您突然这么说......","id":278},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"您的性格。您是一个耐心的、友善的阿戈尔人。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"但这并不会改变您思维上的傲慢。我是指，阿戈尔的傲慢。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#14$1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"所以我并不会以为，我们聊起阻隔层的空洞、地幔的遗迹，甚至人类文明的未来，只是您调节气氛的某种谈话技巧。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不认为阿戈尔会以被动的方式解决问题，弥利亚留姆主动离开固守的本境，只是为了建立另一道防线。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"执政官阁下，你们是否在这条航道上寄予了更深远的目的？","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"......阿戈尔的答案，那个傲慢的答案，我已经告诉了歌蕾蒂娅，您同样有权知晓。","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"“这颗行星仍然存在太多非自然的事物”——而阿戈尔不相信这些事物毫无关联。","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"不论星门与双月这样的奇观，抑或源石与海嗣这样的灾难，都不可能只是突发奇想的产物，它们之间必然存在某种关联。","id":289},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#3$1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"要从源头上解决海嗣问题，杜绝泰拉的危机，意味着要从整体上探明泰拉的本质。陆地上埋藏的秘密，也是其中的一环。","id":291},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"但那都是之后的事情。如果您想问的仅仅是我的答案......","id":293},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"我对航道寄予的唯一希望，就只是让城内的十余万军民，以及格兰法洛的数万惩戒军战士，活着见证阿戈尔的主力进入战场。","id":295},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"charslot","id":297},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":298},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_emgseaalarm","volume":"0.7","id":299},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":300},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":301},{"type":"charslot","id":302},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":303},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_microrobot","id":304},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1401_1#1$1","duration":"0.2","id":305},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"-150,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"0.8","id":306},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“小帮手”","text":"紧急求救信号。","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“小帮手”","text":"来自前往第三十七号巢穴投放信标的舰队。","id":309},{"type":"dialog","id":310},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":312},{"type":"charslot","id":313},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":314},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":315},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":316},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_darkness_03_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":317,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":318},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":319},{"type":"delay","time":"1.3","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你很敏锐。","id":321},{"type":"dialog","id":322},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":323},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"325","text":"你在这里，省得我找你了。"},"2":{"id":"325","text":"你总是这样突然出现又消失吗？"}},"values":[],"id":324},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":325,"end":327},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"关于航道计划，弥利亚留姆向你们透露了多少？","id":327,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":328},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":329},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"331","text":"我以为你会多关心一下歌蕾蒂娅她们。"},"2":{"id":"335","text":"我以为你会稍微关心一下自己的处境。"}},"values":[],"id":330},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":331,"end":334},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"评议会已经证明了她们的清白，更何况还有人愿意帮助她们。","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"回到阿戈尔，回到布局或者阴谋之中，这本来就是歌蕾蒂娅想要的。","id":334},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":335,"end":337},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你我都没被跟踪，也没被监听，这说明我的行踪还没有暴露。","id":337,"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2"],"id":338},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"让我们继续在斗智场没来得及说完的话题。","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"海嗣与阿戈尔的战争已经进行了两百多年，但几乎在同一时间，双方将目光从海洋投向了陆地。","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"整个族群的突然迁徙与整个国家的战争转向，双方行为的背后，或许有同一个深层的原因。","id":342},{"type":"dialog","id":343},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":344},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"346","text":"听起来你对阿戈尔的每一个计划都不信任。"},"2":{"id":"346","text":"乌尔比安，你仍然对我们有所保留。"}},"values":[],"id":345},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":346,"end":355},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"除了已经向歌蕾蒂娅同步过的发现，我确实还知晓更多隐情，这让我不得不更加审慎地看待阿戈尔已经发生和正在进行的一切。","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但这些信息对歌蕾蒂娅来说都为时尚早，你更加无权知情。","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"眼下，我们只需关注航道计划本身。","id":350},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"“一条联通海洋与陆地的航道”......那位医生和伊比利亚审判庭对此都不完全信任，否则你们不会出现在这里。","id":352},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"以高等级武器净空海域，为本境的主力争取通航时间，阿戈尔的战争设计一贯如此简洁高效。","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但城中已经出现了不容忽视的异常情况。","id":355,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":356},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":357},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"359","text":"深海教会？"},"2":{"id":"359","text":"我听说有人失踪了。"}},"values":[],"id":358},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":359,"end":368},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"那位执政官很有些手段。","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"弥利亚留姆远航的这段时间，城市里的堕落者被陆续清除，至今没造成有效的破坏。两支随行军团遭受的损失也远小于预期。","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但现在看来，航道计划进行得有些过于顺利了。","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"在最重要的时间点上，航道计划的相关人员突然失踪，这只会是一个开始。","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我已经在着手调查，我会排除隐患。","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"普通的场所不难进入，我可以规避海巡队的常规巡逻。","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但我担心，问题出现在更核心的地方。","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"不到最后关头，我不想闯进重要项目的研究所或是执政官的冥思间。","id":368,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":369},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":370},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"372","text":"乌尔比安，别把我只当作一个传话筒。"},"2":{"id":"372","text":"乌尔比安，罗德岛需要与你保持合作。"}},"values":[],"id":371},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":372,"end":374},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":374,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":375},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":376},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"378","text":"毕竟，你在城里的行动没那么方便。"},"2":{"id":"378","text":"毕竟，你也是阿戈尔的隐患，不是吗？"}},"values":[],"id":377},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":378,"end":383},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"既是合作，也是监视，很好。","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"还有一件事。","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......斯卡蒂。","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"如果你真的关心深海猎人，看好她。","id":383,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":384},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":385},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":386},{"type":"dialog","id":387},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":388},{"type":"charslot","id":389},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":390},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":391},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sea","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":392},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.3","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":393},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":394},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":395},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","duration":"1","id":396},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"一百五十六艘、一百五十七艘......","id":398,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"这是我见过最紧张的港口枢纽。","id":399,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"这是不是意味着，前线的战况不容乐观？","id":400,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#3$1","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"（哼歌♪）","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"鲨鱼，你居然还有心情唱歌？","id":404,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"为什么不呢？","id":406,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"说不定很快我们也要忙碌起来了。","id":407,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":408},{"type":"charslot","id":409},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","duration":"1","id":410},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":411},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"二队长，你来了。","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"评议会后，你急匆匆地带着凯尔希医生去找克莱门莎执政官，结果如何？","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"很顺利，但我仅仅是个引见者。她们有太多信息要交流，我没必要一直陪着她们。","id":417,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我和克莱门莎简短讨论了深海猎人接下来的具体安排。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"很快，阿戈尔的航道就将正式开启，在此之前，深海猎人将与随弥利亚留姆来到前线的两支军团协同作战。","id":419,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"你看，我的预感没错吧？","id":421,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"嗯。","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"比起待在斗智场里听你们吵来吵去，还是对付那些杂碎来得舒心一些。","id":424,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我们要做什么，以及什么时候出发？","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"具体的指挥权限和战术规划需要与各位军团指挥官进行专门的讨论。","id":427,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"实际上，斯卡蒂——","id":428,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":429},{"type":"charslot","id":430},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":431},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1","id":432},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_emgseaalarm","id":433},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":434},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0.2","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":435},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1398_1#1$1","duration":"0.3","id":436},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"-150,0","posto":"100,0","duration":"0.9","id":437},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":438},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_263_skadi#8","duration":"0.3","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"120,0","id":439},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":440},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":441},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown2","volume":"0.6","id":442},{"type":"delay","time":"0.1","id":443},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"80,0","duration":"0.2","id":444},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":445},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"l","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"喂，这个声音，是紧急军事预警吧？","id":447,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_char_263_skadi_8.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"发生了什么，海嗣侵入了城市？","id":448,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_char_263_skadi_8.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1398_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团士兵","text":"......","id":450},{"type":"charslot","id":451},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我是执政官歌蕾蒂娅，告知我现在的情况。","id":453,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tense_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_tense_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":454,"musicid":3},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1398_1#1$1","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团士兵","text":"是。","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团士兵","text":"第三十七号巢穴的信标投放任务按计划于今天展开，由第十军团的两支舰队负责。","id":457},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团士兵","text":"我们刚刚收到了紧急通讯，他们在前往巢穴的途中遭到了海嗣的袭击。","id":458},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#8","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"海嗣有所准备？","id":460,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_char_263_skadi_8.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1398_1#1$1","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团士兵","text":"目前尚不清楚，消息来得很急，技术院还没来得及给出分析。","id":462},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"港口内此刻是否有待命的小型战斗舰？","id":464,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1398_1#1$1","id":465},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团士兵","text":"时刻都有，您在终端登入就可以调取。","id":466},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":467},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"感谢。接下来的作战中，时刻向我同步遇袭舰队的坐标。深海猎人会在中途脱离舰船，游过战场。","id":468,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1398_1#1$1","id":469},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团士兵","text":"明白。","id":470},{"type":"dialog","id":471},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":472},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","duration":"1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":473},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":474},{"type":"charslot","id":475},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"劳伦缇娜，你与我行动。","id":477,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......斯卡蒂，你留在城市里。","id":478,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#9","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":480,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"二队长？","id":481,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"不要想太多。","id":483,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"陆地与海洋的这次接触至关重要，凯尔希分身乏术。你留下来，保护博士的安全。","id":484,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"这是命令。","id":485,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":486},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"好。","id":487,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":488},{"type":"dialog","id":489},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":490},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":491},{"type":"charslot","id":492},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":493},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":494},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":495,"musicid":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":496},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":497},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":498},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":499},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":500},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":501},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"前面那是......","id":502,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":503},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"劳伦缇娜小姐她们刚回来，就要出城作战吗？","id":504,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":505},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我了解过了，和刚才的警报有关。负责前往第三十七号巢穴投放信标的舰队遭到了海嗣的袭击，她们正准备出发实施救援。","id":506},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"你认识深海猎人？","id":507},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":508},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"嗯。","id":509,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"在陆地上的时候，我们有过短时间的合作，一起经历过一些事情，解决过一些敌人......海嗣。","id":510,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"以她们的脾气和战斗风格，你们能并肩作战......很难得。","id":512},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"如果不是军情紧急，我应该上前跟歌蕾蒂娅执政官打个招呼。她们回到阿戈尔后，我甚至还没有机会正式问候她们。","id":513},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":514},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"每个阿戈尔人都认识深海猎人吗？","id":515,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":516},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......当然不是。我只是曾与她们共事，也曾希望成为她们当中的一员。","id":517},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":518},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"我想起来了，你的队员说过你之前是搞研究的。","id":519,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":520},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我在基因工程领域的课业成果还不错，被选入了深海猎人计划，我的老师是计划的负责人，也是阿戈尔第一位深海猎人。","id":521},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":522},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"当时，符合征召条件的人不多，能改造成功的更少，但他，还有歌蕾蒂娅，已经带领大家取得了惊人的战果。","id":523},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"最令人叹服的一场战役，他们在海底热泉间与海嗣缠斗了整整三天，为两座能源勘探城市争取了宝贵的撤离时间。","id":524},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"海嗣的形态几乎每一天都在变化，在武器使用已经受到严苛管控的当时，他们就是最高效也最保险的军事力量。","id":525},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":526},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我每天看着他们离开，再看着他们回来。","id":527},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我看着他们疲惫地躺进休眠溶胶，等待我替他们记录数据，测试机能，修补身体，那些捷报仿佛和他们没有关系......","id":528},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":529},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我已经忘了自己是怎么想的，反正某一天，我向发展规划所提交了一份主动接受深海猎人改造的申请。","id":530},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":531},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"......换我也会的。","id":532,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":533},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"什么？","id":534},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":535},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"没，我是说，如果是我，也会想要主动提交申请的。","id":536,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":537},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"看着自己的老师、自己身边所有人都在出生入死......谁都会想要追上去吧。","id":538,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":539},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"而且你的身体素质看起来很好，又是项目的研究员，对深海猎人的机能和战斗方式也熟悉......等等，那你为什么？","id":540,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":541},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"因为那份申请被驳回了。","id":542},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":543},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"唔，为什么？","id":544,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":545},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"（摇头）","id":546},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我没去问。我的老师也不会回答这个问题。","id":547},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":548},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"所以你才选择加入海巡队？","id":549,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"海巡队应该是战场上和深海猎人配合最紧密的作战单位吧？","id":550,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":551},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"是......同时负责监视他们。","id":552},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":553},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"......","id":554,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":555},{"type":"charslot","id":556},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":557},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":558},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"巡逻舰已经准备完毕。","id":559},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":560},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"好。","id":561},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"抱歉，艾丽妮，突然说了些不合时宜的事情。","id":562},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":563},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"没关系。","id":564,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":565},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"闲聊结束。军团舰队正在前线与海嗣交锋，但航道数据员的失踪同样关系重大，海巡队的行动照旧。","id":566},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"艾丽妮，你留下来。","id":567},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#2$1","id":568},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"留下来？","id":569,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":570},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我们要去的地方距离前线战场有一定的距离，但依然危险，海巡队有义务保障你的安全。","id":571},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","id":572},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"你想多了，指挥官阁下。","id":573,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"每一个审判官都染过海嗣的血，我不怕它们。","id":574,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":575},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我看过各位的资料，没记错的话，你似乎已经卸任了审判官一职。","id":576},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"感谢你在我们调查时给予的帮助，如我之前所说，你是一个非常敏锐的人......而且勇敢。","id":577},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"但你来到阿戈尔的任务并不是参与作战，回到其他使节身边吧。","id":578},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":579},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"你是想说，阿戈尔与海嗣的战争形态，是来自陆地的我所无法理解的。","id":580,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":581},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......是。","id":582},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","id":583},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"你的担忧没有错，但我此行的目的正是“理解”。","id":584,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"我需要理解阿戈尔，理解海嗣，理解真正的战争，理解海洋深处正在发生的一切......作为一个伊比利亚人。","id":585,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"指挥官阁下，这里已经接近陆地，阿戈尔只有一座城，而这座城面前是整个伊比利亚。","id":586,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"放心，我会量力而行，不会让自己就这么稀里糊涂地死在海洋里。","id":587,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":588},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......艾丽妮，你还这么年轻，从你的表现来看......你应该有一个很好的老师。","id":589},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":590},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"呃，听起来比你的老师好一点？","id":591,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":592},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......帮艾丽妮准备一套深潜装置。","id":593},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"走吧，调查继续。","id":594},{"type":"dialog","id":595},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":596},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":597},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":598},{"type":"image","id":599},{"type":"charslot","id":600}],"characters":["？？？","海嗣","西昆妲","卡西娅","卢契拉","艾丽妮","克莱门莎","凯尔希","“小帮手”","乌尔比安","斯卡蒂","幽灵鲨","歌蕾蒂娅","军团士兵","海巡队队员"]}